metadata.name: Multi-Pep Card #1 #1/20
metadata.description:
In the vast and infinite multiverse,  
  
Beyond the reach of our universe,  

There lie countless worlds to explore,  


With Peps never seen before.

Today we have found a land that's bright as day,  

Where hills are made of croissants flaky,  

And rivers flow with syrup, oh so tasty.


Of breakfast foods a frog was made,  

A creature that was quite unique,  

With eyes of eggs and body of bread,  

A breakfast treat for all to seek.
